<h3 class="bp-subtitle">Monitor Application Health</h3>

<div class="bp-text">
<p>The Administrator Tool includes some basic tools to monitor the health of the application.	After clicking on the <span class="bn-input">Monitor: Health</span> link, the application will perform a series of tests.	The results of these tests will then be displayed.	If the test is successful, then the text <span class="bn-input">OK</span> will be displayed following the test name.	If the test fails, then a link will be provided to display additional information on the results of the test.</p>
</div>